text: Denewulf bisceop & þa hywan on Wintanceastre ænlænað Ælfrede his degXLhida landes æt Alresforda æfter þære læna þe Tunbryht bisceop ær alende his yldran & agan wes on ðæt gerað þet he gesylle ælce geare to hærfestes emnihte ðreo pund to gafole & cyresceattas & cyresceatweorc.
& þenne þæs nuð bið his men beon gearuwe ge to ripe ge to huntoðe.
& efter his dege gange seo ðar umbeflitan into sancte Petre.
Þis synt þara witena hundsetena & ðere hina ðe on þære geðafunge weron.
